node.text: A bear plushie update, as promised! We’ve heard that the plushies are now scheduled to arrive in the warehouse the 1st week of September, and will be distributed to customers the 2nd and 3rd week of September. There have been some shipping delays overseas, unfortunately, which is why they’re arriving a little later than they’d planned - but they’re coming! If anyone needs additional support, or if you have any questions at all about your order,  please contact: support@snapcreative.com 🐻♥️ Thanks again, everyone!

node.text: Bear plushie update! A huge thank you again to everyone who pre-ordered one of these. @snapcreativemfg has been working hard to fulfill all the orders placed, and are set to get them finished & shipped out the end of this month. If anything changes, I’ll post an update here. Thank you so much for your patience, and I hope you love your bear ♥️ Shooby certainly loves hers.
